description: Application for approval of reserved matters pursuant to Condition 2(b) for Buildings B, C, D, E and F, to discharge matters of scale, appearance and landscaping of the outline area, attached to Planning Permission PA/15/02904 (which amended original planning permission ref: PA/10/01864/LBTH) dated October 21st 2016.
